      "rationale": "Normalised RMS error of 8.3% across five operating points is within the 15% acceptance threshold. Systematic bias of −4.1% (CFD under-predicts MIH) is consistent with known limitations of the Giersiepen power-law damage model and is acceptable at MRL 2."
