      "rationale": "RH is the direct comparator used in FDA guidance for predicate device comparisons. Sensitivity analysis confirmed RH varies by 0.08–0.14 per 0.1 mm change in impeller clearance, demonstrating adequate discriminatory power for the tolerance study. QoI is both regulatory-relevant and geometrically sensitive."
